title: What font is this?
content:
Hello all,

I’m new here but thankful you are here. I’m looking for the name of a specific font portrayed in this [font image](http://web.archive.org/web/20091126185925/http:/typophile.com/files/font_24.png). Hopefully I haven’t broken any rules or made anyone mad by my simplistic question and first post. Thanks in advance for any help.

Patrick Chuprina
